== BasecampProjectActivateV1
	This handler allows you to activate an archived project for Basecamp.

=== Parameters
	[Project Name]
		The name of the project you wish to activate.
			
=== Results
	No results are returned for this handler.
	
	An exception is raised if an existing archived project does not exist.

==== Sample Configuration
	Project Name : Board Presentation

=== Detailed Description
	This handler allows you to activate an archived project for Basecamp.
	If there is no archived project that has the has the given name an
	exception will be raised.
	
===  Getting Your User Id Number
	1. In a browser, login to your account.
		here : https://launchpad.37signals.com/basecamp/signin
	2. In the url, your user id comes right after the host name.
		ex. https://basecamp.com/#######/etc
			https://hostname.com/user_id/...
